casebody.data:
Anthony DOVE
v.
WIL-O-WISP APARTMENTS, Owner(s) - John Doe(s), Wil-O-Wisp Apartments Manager, - Jane or Richard Doe, Luby Edward Outlaw, et. al. No. 186P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 12, 2004. Anthony Dove, Pro Se. Kari R. Johnson, Jaye E. Bingham, Raleigh, for Wil-O-Wisp Apartments et al.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiff on the 19th day of July 2004 for rehearing of the decision of this Court pursuant to Rule 31, N.C. Rules of Appellate Procedure, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 12th day of August 2004."
